C***************** input parameters for specsynth *****************************
450   	Npix
3.0   	presel
45000.  R_fac - the spectrograph resolution R=lambda/(Delta lambda)
1.0  	slit - the spectrograph slit width in arcseconds
1       conflag - toggle convolution 1=ON 0=OFF
3.0     conwindo -  # of inst. profile sigma to include in convolution 
3       resfac - (odd integer) sample rate factor for convolution arrays
70.     snr - signal to noise ratio
